original_title: Feeding the Beast: 25 Years of Statesville Haunted Prison
overview: From its humble beginnings as a bunch of theater kids on a farmer's property to the massive, aggressive beast that it ultimately became, watch as a group of friends unknowingly launched what would become one of Chicago's legendary haunted attractions, from the earliest days right up through its very last night on November 6, 2021.
title: Feeding the Beast: 25 Years of Statesville Haunted Prison
